acceptNewKey.description: Label for a button to accept a new safety number

androidMessageLengthWarning.description: Warning that long messages could not get received completely by Android clients.
androidMessageLengthWarning.message: Klien Android hanya akan menerima 2000 karakter pertama dari pesan ini.

changedRecently.description: Shown on confirmation dialog when user attempts to send a message
changedRecently.message: Nomor keamanan Anda dengan $name$ telah berubah baru-baru ini. Ini bisa berarti seseorang mencoba mencegat komunikasi Anda atau bahwa $name$ hanya memasang ulang Sinyal.

changedRecentlyMultiple.description: Shown on confirmation dialog when user attempts to send a message
changedRecentlyMultiple.message: Nomor keamanan Anda dengan beberapa anggota grup telah berubah baru-baru ini. Ini bisa berarti seseorang mencoba mencegat komunikasi Anda atau bahwa mereka hanya memasang ulang Sinyal.

changedRightAfterVerify.description: Shown on the safety number screen when the user has selected to verify/unverify a contact's safety number, and we immediately discover a safety number change
changedRightAfterVerify.message: Nomor keamanan yang ingin Anda verifikasi telah berubah. Harap tinjau nomor keamanan baru Anda dengan $name$. Ingat, perubahan ini bisa berarti seseorang mencoba mencegat komunikasi Anda atau bahwa $name$ hanya memasang ulang Sinyal.

changedSinceVerified.description: Shown on confirmation dialog when user attempts to send a message
changedSinceVerified.message: Nomor keamanan Anda dengan $name$ telah berubah sejak Anda terakhir diverifikasi. Ini bisa berarti seseorang mencoba mencegat komunikasi Anda atau bahwa $name$ hanya memasang ulang Sinyal.

changedSinceVerifiedMultiple.description: Shown on confirmation dialog when user attempts to send a message
changedSinceVerifiedMultiple.message: Nomor keamanan Anda dengan beberapa anggota grup telah berubah sejak terakhir Anda diverifikasi. Ini bisa berarti seseorang mencoba mencegat komunikasi Anda atau bahwa mereka hanya memasang ulang Sinyal.

checkNetworkConnection.description: Obvious instructions for when a user's computer loses its network connection

confirmMigration.message: Start migration process? You will not be able to send or receive Signal messages from this application while the migration is in progress.

connecting.description: Displayed when the desktop client is currently connecting to the server.

debugLogExplanation.message: Catatan ini akan diunggah secara publik agar kontributor dapat melihat. Anda dapat memeriksa kembali dan menyunting ini sebelum mengunggahnya.

deleteConversationConfirmation.description: Confirmation dialog text that asks the user if they really wish to delete the conversation. Answer buttons use the strings 'ok' and 'cancel'. The deletion is permanent, i.e. it cannot be undone.

deleteMessages.description: Menu item for deleting messages, title case.

deleteWarning.message: Apakah kamu yakin? Mengklik 'hapus' akan menghapus pesan ini dari perangkat ini secara permanen.

disappearingMessages.description: Conversation menu option to enable disappearing messages

disconnected.description: Displayed when the desktop client cannot connect to the server.

expiredWarning.description: Warning notification that this version of the app has expired
expiredWarning.message: Versi dari Signal Desktop ini telah kadaluarsa. Mohom memutahirkan ke versi terbaru untuk melanjutkan pengiriman pesan.

export.description: Button to allow the user to export all data from app as part of migration process

exportAgain.description: If user has already exported once, this button allows user to do it again if needed

exportComplete.description: Message shown on the migration screen when we are done exporting data
exportComplete.message:
Your data has been exported to:

$location$

You'll be able to import this data as you set up the new Signal Desktop.

exportError.description: Helper text if the user went forward on migrating the app, but ran into an error
exportError.message: Unfortunately, something went wrong during the export. First, double-check your target empty directory for write access and enough space. Then, please submit a debug log so we can help you get migrated!

exportInstructions.message: The first step is to choose a directory to store this application's exported data. It will contain your message history and sensitive cryptographic data, so be sure to save it somewhere private.

exporting.description: Message shown on the migration screen while we export data
exporting.message: Please wait while we export your data. It may take several minutes. You can still use Signal on your phone and other devices during this time.

failedToSend.message: Gagal mengirim. Cek sambungan jaringan Anda.

fileSizeWarning.message: Maaf, berkas tersebut melebihi batas ukuran pesan.

from.description: Label for the sender of a message

gotIt.description: Label for a button that dismisses a dialog. The user clicks it to confirm that they understand the message in the dialog.

identityChanged.message: Nomor keamanan anda dengan kontak ini telah berubah. Ini bisa berarti ada seseorang mencoba menyadap komunikasi anda, atau kontak telah menghapus aplikasi Signal. Anda mungkin ingin memverifikasi nomor keamanan baru dibawah.

identityKeyErrorOnSend.description: Shown when user clicks on a failed recipient in the message detail view after an identity key change
identityKeyErrorOnSend.message: Nomor keamanan Anda dengan $name$ telah berubah. Ini bisa berarti seseorang mencoba mencegat komunikasi Anda atau bahwa $name$ hanya menginstal ulang Sinyal. Anda mungkin ingin memverifikasi nomor keamanan Anda dengan kontak ini.

installAndroidInstructions.message: Buka Signal di telepon anda dan arahkan ke Pengaturan -> perangkan tersambung. Tekan tombol untuk menambahkan perangkat baru, lalu pindai kode diatas.

installComputerName.description: Text displayed before the input where the user can enter the name for this device.

installConnecting.description: Displayed when waiting for the QR Code

installConnectionFailed.description: Displayed when we can't connect to the server.

installFinalButton.description: The final button for the install process, after the user has entered a name for their device

installFollowUs.message: Ikuti kami untuk pemutakhiran dukungan banyak perangkat di iOS

installGotIt.description: Button for the user to confirm that they have Signal installed.

installIHaveSignalButton.description: Button for the user to confirm that they have Signal for Android

installLinkingWithNumber.description: Text displayed before the phone number that the user is in the process of linking with

installNewSignal.description: When export is complete, a button shows which sends user to Signal Desktop install instructions

installSignalLink.description: Prompt the user to install Signal on Android before linking
installSignalLink.message:
Pertama, pasang Signal di ponsel Android Anda.
Kami akan menautkan perangkat-perangkat Anda dan menjaga pesan-pesan Anda tetap tersinkronisasi.

installSignalLinks.description: Prompt the user to install Signal on their phone before linking
installSignalLinks.message:
Pertama, pasang Signal pada Android atau iPhone anda.
Kami akan menyambungkan perangat anda dan menyelaraskan pesan anda selalu.

installTagline.description: Tagline displayed under 'installWelcome' string on the install page
installTagline.message: Privasi itu mungkin. Signal membuatnya lebih mudah.

installTooManyDevices.message: Maaf, Anda menautkan perangkat terlalu banyak. Coba hapus beberapa.

installWelcome.description: Welcome title on the install page

invalidNumberError.description: When a person inputs a number that is invalid

noLongerVerified.description: Shown in converation banner when user's safety number has changed, but they were previously verified.
